oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Discussion - Fifty Years of ACM Awards - 2014-09-06
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Discussion on the first 50 years of the Academy of Country Music Awards television show from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on September 6, 2014.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Lisa Lee; Bob Romeo; Richard A. “Rac” Clark; Barry Adelman; Clint Black;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Discussion moderated by the Academy of Country Music's Lisa Lee. Participants include Academy of Country Music CEO Bob Romeo, ACM Awards executive producers Richard A. “Rac” Clark and Barry Adelman, and ACM Award winner Clint Black. Includes audio from video.
